======================================================================
PART 3: DOES dp33 DETERMINE α₂?
======================================================================

  At n=7: 3+5=8>7, so only (3,3) disjoint pairs contribute to α₂.
  Therefore α₂ = dp33 (exact equality).
  α₂ == dp33 check: 500/500 match

======================================================================
