======================================================================

  dc3 → possible dp33 values:
    dc3= 1: dp33 = 0 (unique)
    dc3= 2: dp33 = 0 (unique)
    dc3= 3: dp33 ∈ [0, 2] (2 values)
    dc3= 4: dp33 ∈ [0, 1] (2 values)
    dc3= 5: dp33 ∈ [0, 1, 2, 3] (4 values)
    dc3= 6: dp33 ∈ [0, 1, 2, 3] (4 values)
    dc3= 7: dp33 ∈ [0, 1, 2, 3, 4] (5 values)
    dc3= 8: dp33 ∈ [0, 1, 2, 3, 4, 5, 6] (7 values)
